Usage: setObjFPlanBox [-help] <objectType> <objectName> <llx> <lly> <urx> <ury>
                      [-no_snap_to_grid]

-help            # Prints out the command usage
<objectType>     # Object type (string, required)
<objectName>     # Object name (string, required)
<llx>            # lower left x coordinate of the object (float, required)
<lly>            # lower left y coordinate of the object (float, required)
<urx>            # upper right x coordinate of the object (float, required)
<ury>            # upper right y coordinate of the object (float, required)
-no_snap_to_grid # Specify to not honor snap rules (bool, optional)